PATCH for moving GPA Result card to bottom:

In src/app/app.css, after line 91 (.highlight rule), add:

.gpa-result-card {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  margin-top: 2rem;
}

Also modify the .grid rule (around line 36) to add auto-flow:
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
  grid-auto-flow: dense;
  gap: 1.2rem;
}

And make left-column take only 1st column:
.left-column {
  grid-column: 1;
}
